text: Abu Hafs al-Hashimi al-Qurashi (Arabic: أَبُو حَفْصٍ ٱلْهَاشِمِيُّ ٱلْقُرَيْشِيُّ) is the fifth caliph of Daesh. He become caliph on the 3rd or 6th of August 2023, by the spokesperson of Daesh, Abu Hudhayfah Al-Ansari, which came after 4 months after the death of Abu al-Hussein al-Husseini al- Qurashi. == Notes == == References == === Works cited === Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Islamic State people Category:Living people Category:20th-century births
title: Abu Hafs al-Hashimi al-Qurashi
